 * PVE_1_INIT_HT        *    LPDDR_PPP_3_TARG_MT     *   PVE_0_SYSCFG_LT            *                 *
 *                      *                            *   PVE_1_SYSCFG_LT            *                 *                                
 *                      *                            *   PCIE_TARG_SYSCFG           *                 *                                        
